{"tid":1570433,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾國斌：美國國會議員不希望介入香港事務","createTime":"2019-09-15T05:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T06:17:13.000Z","uid":225818,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f050d6307ac8df2782e30b8a39ea400359f96879","tid":1570433,"uid":225818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國國會將審議《香港人權與民主法案》，自由黨黨魁鍾國斌在本台節目《大鳴大放》中，引述部分當地國會議員指，並不希望處理香港問題，擔心若美方介入只會惡化局勢。<br />\n<br />\n鍾國斌又認為即使法案獲通過，對商界不會有太大影響。<br />\n<br />\n對於政府月初宣布撤回修例，鍾國斌認為已是太遲，但總比堅持不撤回好，他相信如短期內可平息動盪，香港經濟可於短期內反彈<br />\n<br />\nSource : NOW新聞 <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=362780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362780&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=c9884c4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362780&h=94eae1a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=362780</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n驚驚豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又對美國內政說三道四<br />\n一齊上twitter話比美國國會議員聽佢地被代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n準備同毒瘤一齊被點名制裁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw呢個法案又唔係針對制裁商人<br />\n對商界影響不大唔係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ddb9f2119c8a3bdb2b1266bc0f57dbb0bca5e3e","tid":1570433,"uid":271917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f050d6307ac8df2782e30b8a39ea400359f96879","tid":1570433,"uid":225818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國國會將審議《香港人權與民主法案》，自由黨黨魁鍾國斌在本台節目《大鳴大放》中，引述部分當地國會議員指，並不希望處理香港問題，擔心若美方介入只會惡化局勢。<br />\n<br />\n鍾國斌又認為即使法案獲通過，對商界不會有太大影響。<br />\n<br />\n對於政府月初宣布撤回修例，鍾國斌認為已是太遲，但總比堅持不撤回好，他相信如短期內可平息動盪，香港經濟可於短期內反彈<br />\n<br />\nSource : NOW新聞 <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=362780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362780&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=c9884c4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362780&h=94eae1a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=362780</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n驚驚豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又對美國內政說三道四<br />\n一齊上twitter話比美國國會議員聽佢地被代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n準備同毒瘤一齊被點名制裁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw呢個法案又唔係針對制裁商人<br />\n對商界影響不大唔係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10d6748e0e7b967f265fd4523026204a7c808d6","tid":1570433,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:39:37.000Z","msg":"Stand with HK, World Anti-totalitarianism March on 29/9/2019<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570427</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\nnew post please help push and upvote"},{"pid":"bc3eacddfa24a361d5e025ddf3425bc2d2aa8858","tid":1570433,"uid":169646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:41:31.000Z","msg":"敵人反對的...... <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74cb452d5154c8818f75ca47d9a8c24595c73a8f","tid":1570433,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:17:13.000Z","msg":"引